uml;z CV-nizi ir@kontakt.az e-mail &uuml;nvanına g&ouml;ndərə bilərsiniz.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vacancy:&nbsp;<strong>Fəhlə</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tələblər:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; fiziki cəhətdən g&uuml;cl&uuml; olmalı&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; məsulliyyətli, punktual, komandada işləmək bacarığı</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vəzifələr:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; mağazaya daxil olan malların boşaldılması, yerləşdirilməsi<br />\r\n&bull; təhl&uuml;kəsizlik qaydalarına əməl etmək<br />\r\n&bull; rəhbərlik tərəfindən verilən digər tapşırıqların yerinə yetirilməsi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>İş şəraiti:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; AR Əmək Məcəlləsinə əsasən sənədləşmə<br />\r\n&bull; İş g&uuml;n&uuml;: 6 g&uuml;n, 1 g&uuml;n istirahət<br />\r\n&bull; Əmək haqqı 400 AZN</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yuxarıda qeyd olunan tələblərə uyğun namizədlərdən<em><strong>&nbsp;012 4496793/ 4496794</strong>&nbsp;</em>n&ouml;mrələri ilə əlaqə saxlamaq və ya m&ouml;vzu yerində &ldquo;&nbsp;<strong>Fəhlə</strong>&nbsp;&rdquo; qeyd edərək CV-nizi ABC-Telecom&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:hr@abc-telecom.az\" title=\"hr@abc-telecom.az\"><strong>hr@abc-telecom.az</strong></a>elektron &uuml;nvanına g&ouml;ndərməyiniz xahiş olunur.</p>\r\n','','2019-08-01','2019-08-09','','',1),(19,19,'az','Education Manager','<p><strong>Education Manager</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duties of the Education Manager include:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Supervise all preparations for the course, manage classroom set up, equipment and software.<br />\r\n&bull; In a team, organize, plan and budget for new courses, facilities, equipment and human resources.<br />\r\n&bull; Present all course materials in an effective fashion.<br />\r\n&bull; Work on new and update/modify the existing STEAM (Science, Technology, Engineering, Art, Math) content.<br />\r\n&bull; Research, initiate, manage and/or prepare new course materials.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; Communicate courteously and effectively with a diverse group of course participants, instructors and administration of educational centers.<br />\r\n&bull; Consider and instruct the trainers accordingly about the participants&rsquo; needs and learning styles.<br />\r\n&bull; Ensure provision of all pre- and post-course paperwork and reports, including appropriate documents of educational content.<br />\r\n&bull; Plan for final project demonstrations and issue certificates to students in a timely manner.<br />\r\n&bull; Plan for promotional and educational activities, workshops, seasonal camps, etc.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&bull; Provide course oversight including the instructional components for new instructors.<br />\r\n&bull; Recognize discrepancies and develop solutions.<br />\r\n&bull; Develop and implement course quality standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Requirements of the role:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; At least 2 years of experience in educational management.<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent written and spoken Azeri, Russian and English.<br />\r\n&bull; Excellent communication skills.<br />\r\n&bull; Interest in innovations, digital technologies and education.<br />\r\n&bull; Experience and/or desire to work with educators, children and educational institutions.<br />\r\n&bull; Responsibility, attention to details and ability to work in a team environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Terms and conditions:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 40 hours per week (full-time job)<br />\r\n&bull; Compliance with the requirements of the Labor Code</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All interested candidates may submit their CVs to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:egtconsult@outlook.com\" title=\"egtconsult@outlook.com\"><strong>egtconsult@outlook.com</strong></a>&nbsp;along. Please indicate &ldquo;<strong>Education Manager</strong>&rdquo; in the subject line.</p>\r\n','','2019-08-04','2019-08-22','','',1),(20,19,'ru','Education Manager','<p><strong>Education Manager</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duties of the Education Manager include:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Supervise all preparations for the course, manage classroom set up, equipment and software.<br />\r\n&bull; In a team, organize, plan and budget for new courses, faciliti